short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Allows you to export mode tables to a csv

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows you to export Mode tables in explorations to a CSV! This extension is for you if you've ever created a Mode Exploration, and then have been dismayed at finding out you can't export the exploration table you've made to a CSV.
